    "Figure 6 below reports optimal model for each widow size.",
    "The ANN layer uses the LSTM extracted features to classify component status with a sigmoid activation and 1 unit output.",
    "The system, combined with a binary cross-entropy loss function, quickly learns to predict component Table 1 reports the Artificial Neural Network (ANN) classification results for all the chosen n horizons.",
    "The model correctly predicted 88.98% of the next downtime across a horizon of 720 observations, with 99.19% of the healthy observations and 88.69% of the failure cases correctly predicted.",
    "The model precision is 99.97% which is the proportion of cases predicted as failure cases that are failures."
